sect1.para:
While a user can certainly enter reversing transactions manually, &appname; includes a menu option (
TransactionAdd Reversing Transaction
) that can quickly create the reversing transaction for you. This option only appears when you are in an account register. When you are in the transaction that needs to be reversed, all you need to do is select this menu item, and a duplicate transaction that reverses the active transaction is immediately created.

